      <datafield ind1="0" ind2=" " tag="505">
         <subfield code="a">Creativity out of difference : theorising the semiotic, social and temporal origin of creative acts -- Creativity as symbolic transformation -- Creative engagement across the lifespan -- Canonical affordances and creative agency -- Life creativity : imagining one's life -- The creativity of the social : imagination, development and social change in Rio de Janeiro's favelas -- Creativity and the generative approach to culture and meaning -- The socio-materiality of creativity : a case study of the creative processes in design work -- Discussing creativity from a cultural psychological perspective.</subfield>
      </datafield>
